ed="T" n="0719a18"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0719a18"/><head><date from-iso="+0689-12-21" key="j19730671978610" to-iso="+0705-02-24">周</date><placeName key="PL000000042305">西京廣福寺</placeName><persName key="A000332">日照</persName>傳<ptr target="#n97"/></head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0719a19"/><persName key="A000332">釋地婆訶羅</persName>，<name>華</name>言<persName key="A000332">日照</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000048208">中印度</placeName>人也。洞明<lb
ed="T" n="0719a20"/>八藏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g335"/>，博曉五明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g88"/>，戒行高<anchor xml:id="beg0719sgsz1"/>奇<anchor xml:id="end0719sgsz1"/>，學業勤悴<ptr type="glossary" target="#g336"/>，而呪術<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g337"/><lb
ed="T" n="0719a21"/>尤工。以<persName key="A002146">天皇</persName><date from-iso="+0650-02-10" key="j19585081970910" to-iso="+0684-01-25">時</date>來遊此<ref target="#PL000000000106" type="place">國</ref>，<date from-iso="+0679-06-17" key="j19692271969255" to-iso="+0679-07-15"><name>儀鳳</name>四年五月</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0719a22"/>表請翻度所齎經夾，仍準<persName key="A000294">玄奘</persName>例，於一大<lb
ed="T" n="0719a23"/>寺別院安置，并大德三五人同譯。至<persName key="A002099">天后</persName><date key="j19723801972741" notBefore-iso="+0688-02-03" notAfter-iso="+0689-01-29"><name>垂<lb
ed="T" n="0719a24"/>拱</name>末</date><ptr target="#n338"/>，於<ref target="#PL000000042324 #PL000000023665" type="place">兩京東西<name>太原寺</name></ref>（<placeName key="PL000000042324">西太原寺</placeName>後改<placeName key="PL000000042324">西崇福寺</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000023665">東太原寺</placeName>後改<lb
ed="T" n="0719a25"/><placeName key="PL000000023665">大福先寺</placeName>），及<placeName key="PL000000042305">西京廣福寺</placeName><ptr target="#n339"/>，譯《大乘顯識經》<ptr target="#n98"/>、《大乘五<lb
ed="T" n="0719a26"/>蘊論》<ptr target="#n104"/>等凡一十八部，沙門<persName key="A002106">戰陀</persName><ptr target="#n340"/>、<persName key="A008982">般若提婆</persName>譯<lb
ed="T" n="0719a27"/>語，沙門<persName key="A001727">慧智</persName>證<name>梵</name>語<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g52"/>。勅諸名德助其法化<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g341"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0719a28"/>沙門<persName key="A008984">道成</persName>、<persName key="A008985">薄塵</persName>、<persName key="A008981">嘉尚</persName>、<persName key="A001414">圓測</persName>、<persName key="A008979">靈辯</persName>、<persName key="A000661">明恂</persName>、<persName key="A008977">懷度</persName>證<lb
ed="T" n="0719a29"/>義，沙門<persName key="A008976">思玄</persName>、<persName key="A001192">復禮</persName>綴文筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>，<persName key="A002099">天后</persName>親敷叡藻，<pb ed="T" n="0719b" xml:id="T50.2061.0719b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0719b01"/>製序冠首焉。<persName key="A000332">照</persName>甞與<persName key="A000438">覺護</persName>同翻《佛頂》<ptr target="#n342"/>，深體<lb
ed="T" n="0719b02"/><name>唐</name>言，善傳佛意。每進新經，錫賚豐厚。後終<lb
ed="T" n="0719b03"/>于翻經小房，享年七十五<ptr target="#n343"/>。<persName key="A002099">天后</persName>勅葬于<placeName key="PL000000023650">洛陽<lb
ed="T" n="0719b04"/>龍門香山</placeName>，塔見存焉。</p>
